{"id":249358,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/global-voices-沙特阿拉伯：奔向性别平等的终点线/","date":"2012-08-29T21:30:19Z","modified":"2012-08-29T21:30:19Z","title":"Global Voices | 沙特阿拉伯：奔向性别平等的终点线","content":"<p><p>此次伦敦奥运，沙特阿拉伯有两名女性选手获准参加，尽管值得表扬，博客《沙国女性驾车》(<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.saudiwomendriving.blogspot.com/\" href=\"http://www.saudiwomendriving.blogspot.com/\">Saudi Women Driving</a>)仍然为沙国禁止女性开车的现况深表遗憾。</p>\n<p>《沙国女性驾车》说：“世界都在关注沙国女性在奥运亮眼的一面，而许多新闻里有提到，她们回到自己国内，连车也开不了。”</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://blog.amnestyusa.org/middle-east/game-on-for-saudi-women/\" href=\"http://blog.amnestyusa.org/middle-east/game-on-for-saudi-women/\">国际特赦组织美国分会的博客</a>也点出：“沙特阿拉伯要穿越性别平等的终点线，肯定还有好长一段路要走。”话虽如此，2012奥运，Sarah Attar所跑的这段女子800公尺，也确实向前迈了好大一步。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%94%E5%90%91%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E7%82%B9%E7%BA%BF&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F30%2F11389%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F30%2F11389%2F&#038;desc=%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E9%98%BF%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%94%E5%90%91%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%88%E7%82%B9%E7%BA%BF\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F30%2F11389%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org